      <title>精神航空寻求破产以与 Frontier 合并</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/spirit-air-pursues-bankruptcy-as-a-path-to-tie-up-with-frontier</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，精神航空公司 (Spirit Airlines Inc.) 正在与 Frontier Group Holdings Inc. 商谈申请破产以便于竞争对手廉价航空公司进行收购。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/spirit-air-pursues-bankruptcy-as-a-path-to-tie-up-with-frontier</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 23 Oct 2024 21:22:50 GMT</pubDate>
