    <item>
      <title>美国大选将促进加密货币参与度提高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-23/us-election-will-lead-to-better-crypto-engagement</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Ripple Labs Inc. 首席执行官 Brad Garlinghouse 表示，无论美国大选结果如何，我们都会与加密货币行业进行更具建设性的接触。他在“Bloomberg Crypto”节目中与 Sonali Basak 和 Tim Stenovec 进行了交谈。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-23/us-election-will-lead-to-better-crypto-engagement</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 23 Oct 2024 21:20:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
