      <title>最高法院阻止邦吉集团对阿根廷大豆出口商的救助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/court-ruling-sets-back-bunge-s-bg-rescue-of-argentina-soy-exporter-vicentin</link>
      <description><![CDATA[最高法院的一项裁决阻止了邦吉全球公司 (Bunge Global SA) 对维森丁 SAIC 的困境收购，维森丁 SAIC 曾是阿根廷庞大的大豆加工行业的皇冠上的明珠。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/court-ruling-sets-back-bunge-s-bg-rescue-of-argentina-soy-exporter-vicentin</guid>
